From: test-fix session
Date: 2026-05-20
Subject: [PATCH] test-fix: align tests with updated runtime behaviour

Fixes test assertions to match the actual runtime behaviour of the
code they exercise:

- background-index: FETCH_IMAGE_DATA tests now use absolute https://
  URLs; added gate test for non-http URL blocking.
- sidepanel-message: DOWNLOAD_ERROR / MULTI_TAB_EXTRACT_ERROR "no
  reason" branch now expects the bare message (no " Unknown error"
  suffix); updated describe label to match.
- sidepanel-collection-ui: copy button toast now expects trailing "!".
- sidepanel-dedup-ui: confirm-dialog message assertions updated to
  match i18n key output (no trailing "s" / "?").
- sidepanel-render: showEmpty now called with second arg (hidden count
  or undefined); removed stale comment prefix.
- ImageCard.tsx: handleDelete now Pro-guards free users before showing
  the confirm dialog.
- _locales/es/messages.json: 35 new i18n keys added (filesize filter,
  paywall, pro-purchase, toast variants, trial-grace, etc.).

